short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Brings back the undo and redo buttons in Webflow Designers Navbar.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: UndoFlow is your go-to Chrome extension for bringing back the indispensable undo and redo functionalities right within Webflow's interface. Whether you're a designer or developer, UndoFlow integrates seamlessly, enhancing your workflow and ensuring that no mistake sets you back. Experience a more forgiving and flexible design process with UndoFlow!
